<h3>GAP - a system for computational discrete algebra</h3>
<p>
	<b>site:</b> <a href="https://www.gap-system.org/">https://www.gap-system.org/</a>
</p>
<p>
	GAP is a system for computational discrete algebra. I primarily make use of the <a href="https://www.gap-system.org/Packages/semigroups.html">semigroups package</a> for playing with diagram semigroups computationally.
